or people with disabilities to rise out of poverty and into lives of prosperity.</li><li>All people have the capacity, individually or with support to make meaningful choices about their lives.</li><li>How management supports their staff is directly reflected in how staff support the people they serve.</li><li>All people have talents and knowledge to create welcoming, rich and diverse communities for everyone.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"center\",\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center has-black-color has-text-color\"><strong>Who is Choice Powers Change</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":50,\"width\":384,\"height\":276,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-rounded\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img src=\"https://choice-powers-change-consulting.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/marlene-rachael.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-50\" width=\"384\" height=\"276\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">Rachael Newkirk</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Rachael Newkirk has worked as a Service Coordinator and now, Case Management Supervisor at a regional center for 21 years. She also has experience working for the Department of Rehabilitation conducting work skills assessments. Rachael worked in a house where four adults lived together, as the house administrator. She worked as a direct support person to help people with disabilities reclaim their lives after living in a state hospital, and with seniors who want to continue to live in their own home.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">Marlene McCollum</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Marlene McCollum has worked as a Service Coordinator and now, Case Management Supervisor at regional centers for 19 years. Marlene has worked with infants in the Early Start Program and with adults living in an array of living settings. In addition, she worked as a vocational counselor for an agency where people with disabilities gained work experience in a variety of employment programs. She has also worked with women in crisis who needed safety and support.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":28,\"sizeSlug\":\"medium\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-medium\"><img src=\"https://choice-powers-change-consulting.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Hands-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"Picture of hands\" class=\"wp-image-28\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','13-revision-v1','','','2020-10-16 23:27:30','2020-10-16 23:27:30','',13,'https://choice-powers-change-consulting.local/13-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
